#inline#mFMb_DS_GetTrigger( { idleMode } )/*	What it does:	Gets the currently set evaluation formula for a optionally given idle mode.		Required parameters:	none. Gets the formula for userNotIdle when no parameter has been passed to the formula.		Optional parameters:	"userIdle", "userNotIdle", "scriptPaused", "scriptRunning" or "unSafe"		returns:	a formula as text		could return myFMbutler error 7 / Evaluation Error 1224		notes:	returns the last formula that has been set using mFMb_DS_SetTrigger()*/